\f0\b\fs52 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Modular movie notification system\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
To get instant alerts on your phone whenever your server experiences a system crash, recovery event, or ad swap, you can integrate a 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Discord Webhook
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  directly into your shell script. Discord webhooks are completely free, highly reliable, and take less than two minutes to set up.\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa80\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 1. Set Up Your Discord Webhook Channel\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Open Discord on your desktop or mobile app.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	2.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Go to your personal server settings (or create a private server just for your stream updates).\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	3.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Click on 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Integrations
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  > 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Webhooks
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  > 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 New Webhook
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 .\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	4.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Name the webhook something like "Stream Monitor Bot" and assign it to a text channel.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	5.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Click 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Copy Webhook URL
